tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE competitors_seo_strategies (
  competitor_id INT NOT NULL,
  competitor_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  seo_strategy TEXT,
  analysis_date DATE,
  PRIMARY KEY (competitor_id)
);

CREATE TABLE competitor_seo_strategies (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  competitor_name VARCHAR(255),
  keyword VARCHAR(100),
  ranking_position INT,
  analysis_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE own_seo_tactics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  tactic_name VARCHAR(255),
  implementation_date DATE,
  success_metric VARCHAR(100),
  notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE keyword_performance (
    keyword_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    keyword VARCHAR(50),
    search_volume INT,
    organic_ranking INT,
    competitor_id INT REFERENCES competitor_data(competitor_id)
);

CREATE TABLE backlink_quality (
    backlink_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    backlink_url VARCHAR(255),
    domain_authority INT,
    referring_domains INT,
    competitor_id INT REFERENCES competitor_data(competitor_id)
);

CREATE TABLE rankings (
    ranking_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    competitor_id INTEGER REFERENCES competitors(competitor_id),
    keyword_id INTEGER REFERENCES keywords(keyword_id),
    position INTEGER NOT NULL,
    date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE backlinks (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    competitor_id INT,
    backlink_url STRING,
    anchor_text STRING,
    authority_score INT
);
